lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;摩根大通一直在测试&lt;/strong&gt;一系列由人工智能驱动的投资代理，这些代理可以根据不断变化的市场状况在股票和债券之间进行转换。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/2vzd_bsbB_ni23iZjcyo7yUcNp_IIyQUQFnXS6pg0pai6RNZ4DzuGFR8Ds7Dn0hfGafWRwmChYx0EkJYU3t4s5UXIXJRiwPKGmk1TC--dKI9RybcwilnNk8fICeA-ADIG5x0lK6DKyCKJE4XqkcARDESLzFf-8LiJttsMyBipWsE1VuhengUxD7VK7JlIcJeHE2O_22EiAo5fqXeMYGewK-8Tyh4SRiER5sc3w9O1HADkNk9ojcYKNmjoxhfUtbS88uMDWakyI5SO7PygrkSKwMuoEjNVweQjX3lNYWYcSfOZ7bPWq8gy1Kkqxtp3iANlRKqu2Z4xgVSX9Lq2gF9p5tbx8ncknLmKicKZsh4ihu4HMSHPYKTrx_vgNbJFIokJKKDzKTsDXaiTNHebv1v15BnE0wna2-4ZSbDNRxJHSPSvndMtwzSUpApnAsPwOKyJepsiF_U78-IXUCL1KqATEC-Tj01Jyk7vLEy0s6pUJJT7ted6Mgjl5YJs7kn0tUuF4hILKddfxyKaPNBFEBPmu1oiY7rWwGMRbR0Ry-QzFFs402MJXVkjYvB/GuCBpP_YO210pautaEG-fTHFva9LL38F/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="摩根大通构建的人工智能代理在回测中击败了 60/40 的投资组合"&gt;早期结果令人鼓舞&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;然而，尽管越来越多的证据&lt;/strong&gt;表明人工智能的广泛采用可能会让投资者更快、更了解情况，但它也引发了人们对如果每个人都转向这些模型会对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ocQhS8KBs-h7lc07zeatfv2tLizRIszXGF7tPKPeGO1_HZksikcmhMqGr04ZXzORN3R6YJYvUdtbkUwj9-Yco2UvJnLDL-gvEVc6xbRpm-BeKN3On61YlHmJx6DjkdiAq9wXgC9Qcfnx8GatkyNiHs4yPZk0hh3DCbIrs20OJomVWMz0pjEa7ux4e_gFKk9NmqfVan0Zf0O_NAMTI_BxyXbPJZ_aSIE5r87eECvKgFM55QvRUY7DXUTRRxeSPjyaiEF8YyEeJxfUu9tzcFdbTB5ogBPXcpMnRCuHpIGatN57PXSXsT1IALebmQeM0K86OahAPTYn-zSRq-QM888-MAE6g9xlF2PIhv5fToeIVACPLB8-EvCluWOXIc1002uFTRMdCTTqA-wSVFMHtYoxpii7tv2bQSKxAPvAs_1BZ8K0c3ENlRUTegdYwf5C8NLaaY8yDCz-8lsJpwjAJB6QR6emjlaAJyHTP35XW_pjmSizfdokKwkH1lyuBxQEJU_S2iXYeq1A7oHweAFn3q0WsAntHemGhuZONScpmicZRMeD0_8Gmoxh/SaVNAy98jt_RJyJIjLn_HmQndzqj05dH/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-