kCg0XrJpbsDJNsFXZ_1X6G1b3ayaWC3uNOgynvqvB1PCBv-60wNYhswnbGSdlX1E-KofyBP_b1h-_cDNebipmfhQl6yjP9rwpBe7CmurtxmYPXcQmFsAAEHcZAQ/8kujS_FFTSpz-KymaA1zw_zrC1z_tU_9/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="五角大楼保持沉默，美联社重现美国袭击导致 100 多名伊朗儿童死亡的事件"&gt;在此过程中造成数千人死亡&lt;/a&gt;，特朗普现在表示停火已经结束，进一步的外交将毫无意义。但钱皮恩写道，尽管伊朗试图扩大其对这条重要水道的影响力，但特朗普和美国海湾盟友的麻烦实际上源于他自己的谎言。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;不管特朗普怎么说，美国并没有赢得战争。伊朗也没有按照任何定义投降，更不用说“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/fLMXIBsPpjSHSArKG-pISE41sfr8ZDt8Iu6w3cVfBj71oDDmYh_DfOUxN0jqqEc0yfw0K0E14kWKL1ZmOtNGFMzDYahakBP5VwzkaM7eQcpH6ZI-WisM9Ekw8EVYwjok-ytEv3HEf0i1jwOUon2r1wuFHjeO55FGIaOMxg3wm5TfCdvMbUePKtqqKyiklDF9QwZXrr45o9KBvIaCC_Iu3AA8IIwowuuIro3rr6bbAQYaj-ELlBKwS1Cd1GtVbWmWCJjZoa0FzWx5UV9fGcafSw7-r0_vDYgV3vbuf5dBuDrWe1TKPQ7Evv_9pAwI_NQItFdwQErfte8KSEKchpPVFqRY73M65C_Lm3YTY6nad8HfsX74UBgz0P6ZFRPCweu50F85AVB3550SUe7naEG5EQwmq3Ac3hpQvAHn6Ze9Fn6kHm_cCiVf56yZ-fHMCbid8_4WEYTmTnJFyGNXSpZyzxE64qOtXHkJuSMbCu1F94vr94hbauza4aS2f5GMYAOzVKq84xsUdlRoBDrXaKq43TU/bBuAiz67QoSzfXp8-HRziSbUaQunP9nL/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普希望“无条件投降”，不会寻求与伊朗达成协议"&gt;无条件&lt;/a&gt;”投降了。事实上， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/M8LCzv_kGNP2JhmHsylO6VIXDFztiGffYCG75CY1fOUHqJF3Xw38GJvBkKD8nvwv8hiDy6468UXQQljh0PXK2LsOS9DEyRITVn8NCGoVwaS110STjg58LykgTkOgdMp6UFfHbzgsdSTPyGYppY7wL7ZUqowzMnk-6nM3cXRPkh5SZ0VhwoTX7uNlJuGj1lmMcAr57VS6ZuIk03rJpDLg894fJfZBichopaG20Fb02rf-KkTAl8ZeMyoMwfAJB7eg8dQV4XOWrOap-8cv1eFNUi-2pE2a5CjAKiabIbnxSDbvMt2K4UXgHbhvOVXmDviIDeEdOYa-4nfzlvoLiiJiOfJkZqN4RXGd3EYq2_JYRiRdEGEu5Iv7uT-rIJq2evJLnIlhrGvNTb_8OkljWlV5NKCY1doDWUxHHUdk6e4B2_j23J_BE-XtTWsr6lMScSdcat4WYyYI6YJBMktGJo4PH8qW8NACfQmrPirvu3OoA8BNMNfVvRBstlJXn7FuV0MDjPszhTk/_H0_5TIhl8KqMcjr95-gwPPD3KOVLrjK/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普表示伊朗停战结束，未来将有更多袭击，油价突破 80 美元"&gt;